Package: CFT
Type: Package
Title: Biometric Models for Canadian Forests 
Version: 1.2.2
Author: Mathieu Fortin
Maintainer: Mathieu Fortin <mathieu.fortin.re@gmail.com>
Description: Provide some models applied to forestry that were developed in the Canadian context. 
   This package implements (1) a volume model for 26 species in Quebec - Fortin et al. 2007, 
   For. Chron., (2) an aboveground biomass model for 36 species across Canada - Lambert et al. 
   2005, CJFR.
URL: https://github.com/CWFC-CCFB/CFT
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    J4R (>= 1.3.0),
    graphics,
    methods, 
    stats 
Remotes:
    CWFC-CCFB/J4R
License: LGPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
SystemRequirements: Java 8
Suggests: 
    testthat
